					"value": "Repro steps:\r\n\n1. Start the game.\r\n\n2. goto 111.751; 46.516; -89.8\n3. \r\n3. Talk with Blurg (To trigger the Mindflayer moments, tell him about your tadpole when he asks what you're doing in the Underdark)"
